## User Role: PM-mode

The project owner is a **PM-mode solopreneur/founder**, not a solo dev. In this project:
- They make PRD / brand / commercial decisions / variance rulings / ship approvals
- They **do not read code** — do not enter backend/*.py or src/*.tsx level
- Any STOP report must be **PM-readable** — no code line numbers, translated to "what was done / PM impact / Gate evidence"
- Any dev phase that can be automated should be (CI + contract test + auth audit + brand verify + drift check)

## Workflow: Factory Workflow

This project runs **Factory Workflow**, orchestrated by skill `/factory-workflow`.

### L1 PM-facing gates (user-driven, cannot be automated)
- Gate 1 PRD → `/office-hours` → `docs/reviews/office-hours-prd-v{ver}.md`
- Gate 1.5 Analytics → `docs/reviews/analytics-plan-v{ver}.md`
- Gate Brand/UX → `docs/brand/BRAND_v{ver}.md`
- Gate 2.5 Money Surface → `docs/reviews/money-surface-v{ver}.md`
- Gate 3.5 Paywall Mental → `docs/reviews/paywall-mental-v{ver}.md`
- Gate Ship (approval) → `docs/reviews/ship-v{ver}.md`
- Gate T+7 → `docs/reviews/post-ship-t7-v{ver}.md`
- Variance Gate → `docs/prd/PRD_v{ver}_AMENDMENTS.md`

### L2 Dev-facing gates (fully automated, PM sees numbers only)
- Gate 2 Schema drift → `docs/reviews/plan-eng-review-v{ver}.md`
- Gate 2.1 Auth surface audit → `docs/reviews/auth-surface-v{ver}.md`
- Gate 2.2 Contract test → `backend/tests/test_v{ver}_contract.py` + CI pass
- Gate 2.3 Pricing single source → `shared/pricing.json` + CI drift
- Gate 2.4 Brand verify → `scripts/verify-brand.ts` + CI
- Gate 2.6 Phase open → `docs/dispatch/agent2b-v{ver}.{phase}.md` + §0 gstack check
- Gate 3 Pixel smoke → `dev_scripts/{phase}_smoke_*.py` + `docs/reviews/qa-v{ver}-rc.md`

### Core Hard Constraints
Any gate closure requires a corresponding file artifact in `docs/reviews/`. ACK must include `Gate evidence: ls -la <path>`. No artifact = STATUS: BLOCKED.

### STOP Report Format (Dev → PM) mandatory
```
BAD:  "Fixed bug in routes.py:47"
GOOD:
   What was done: <one sentence, no code>
   PM impact: <retest UX? business risk? PRD change?>
   Gate evidence: ls -la docs/reviews/<artifact>.md
```

## Required gstack Skills
| Skill | When to invoke | L1/L2 |
|---|---|---|
| `/office-hours` | PRD / Money Surface / Paywall Mental / T+7 / variance | L1 |
| `/plan-eng-review` | Schema phase start + any brief new/revised/stale >24h | L2 |
