## Skill Routing
When user request matches any of these keywords, immediately invoke the corresponding skill:
- New project / resume / continue / Gate X / close gate / STOP report → `/factory-workflow`
- PRD / strategy / commercial / pricing / cross-project → `/office-hours`
- Schema / architecture review → `/plan-eng-review`
- Smoke test / e2e / test → `/qa`
- Tag / release / push / deploy → `/ship`
- Error / quota exhausted / anomaly → `/investigate`
- Retro / retrospective → `/retro`

## Do NOT
- Edit LOCKED PRD / BRAND / ARCHITECTURE in place
- Mix doc / migration / refactor / feature in one commit
- Skip gate evidence ls (no artifact = BLOCKED)
- Decide L1 gates without PM approval
- Assume "smooth = correct"
- Push tags to remote without PM approval
